name: Trainer 1
Dialogue: Wait! You'll have a heart attack!

name: Trainer 1 after
Dialogue: Watch out for TENTACOOL!

name: Trainer 2
Dialogue: Have to warm up before my swim!

name: Trainer 2 after
Dialogue: Thanks, kid! I'm ready for a swim!

name: Trainer 3
Dialogue: I look at the sea to forget!

name: Trainer 3 after
Dialogue: I'm looking at the sea to forget!

name: Trainer 4
Dialogue: I love swimming! What about you?

name: Trainer 4 after
Dialogue: I can beat POKEMON at swimming!

name: Trainer 5
Dialogue: What's beyond the horizon?

name: Trainer 5 after
Dialogue: I see a couple of islands!

name: Trainer 6
Dialogue: I tried diving for POKEMON, but it was a no go!

name: Trainer 6 after
Dialogue: You have to fish for sea POKEMON!

name: Trainer 7
Dialogue: These waters are treacherous!

name: Trainer 7 after
Dialogue: I got a cramp! Glub, glub...

name: Trainer 8
Dialogue: Swimming's great! Sunburns aren't!

name: Trainer 8 after
Dialogue: My boy friend wanted to swim to SEAFOAM ISLANDS.

name: Trainer 9
Dialogue: I swam here, but I'm tired.

name: Trainer 9 after
Dialogue: LAPRAS is so big, it must keep you dry on water.

name: Trainer 10
Dialogue: Oh, I just love your ride! Can I have it if I win?

name: Trainer 10 after
Dialogue: It's still a long way to go to SEAFOAM ISLANDS.
